headline: With the Potential for Extreme Heat, PSE&G Is Prepared and Urges Customers to Stay Safe and Energy Smart
summary: With temperatures expected to climb this weekend and into next week, and the National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration (NOAA) forecasting above-average temperatures across the Mid-Atlantic this summeri, PSE&G is prepared and is encouraging customers to take steps now to stay safe, conserve energy and manage their bills.
